
AsyncTask help use UI thread easier
It allows to perform bground operation, publish result on UI thread without having to manipulate threads / handlers

3 generic types
AsyncTask<Params, Progress, Result>
can be AsyncTask<Void, Void, Void>

4 steps: onPreExecute, doInBackground, onProgressUpdate, onPostExecute
onPreExecute: invoked on UI thread immediately after the task is executed.

